{"title":"通过PicGo&GitHub搭建个人图床","uid":"652ae16e072fc0f40f3802df81773ad3","slug":"通过PicGo-GitHub搭建个人图床","date":"2023-01-10T06:25:13.000Z","updated":"2023-01-10T07:16:51.623Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/通过PicGo-GitHub搭建个人图床.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/wiceee/myimg/main/img/20230110142616.png","content":"<h1 id=\"通过PicGo-amp-GitHub搭建个人图床\"><a href=\"#通过PicGo-amp-GitHub搭建个人图床\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"通过PicGo&amp;GitHub搭建个人图床\"></a>通过PicGo&amp;GitHub搭建个人图床</h1><h2 id=\"下载PicGo\"><a href=\"#下载PicGo\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"下载PicGo\"></a>下载PicGo</h2><ul>\n<li>点击<a href=\"https://github.com/Molunerfinn/PicGo\">这里</a>进入以下界面，点击<strong>releases</strong></li>\n<li><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/wiceee/myimg/img/image-20230110143051324.png\" alt=\"image-20230110143051324\"></li>\n<li>找到<code>Assets</code>点开，根据系统下载对应版本，我是Windows 10，下载的标有红框的版本</li>\n<li><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/wiceee/myimg/img/image-20230110143530352.png\" alt=\"image-20230110143530352\"></li>\n<li>下载好后默认安装即可</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"创建GitHub仓库\"><a href=\"#创建GitHub仓库\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"创建GitHub仓库\"></a>创建GitHub仓库</h2><ul>\n<li>新建一个仓库，用来存图片</li>\n<li><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/wiceee/myimg/img/image-20230110143759407.png\" alt=\"image-20230110143759407\"></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"设置PicGo\"><a href=\"#设置PicGo\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"设置PicGo\"></a>设置PicGo</h2><ul>\n<li>打开PicGo，点开<strong>PicGo设置</strong>，翻到最底下选择图床类型</li>\n<li><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/wiceee/myimg/img/image-20230110143935124.png\" alt=\"image-20230110143935124\"></li>\n<li>点开<strong>图床设置</strong>下的<strong>GitHub</strong>，新建一个设置</li>\n<li><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/wiceee/myimg/img/image-20230110144044707.png\" alt=\"image-20230110144044707\"></li>\n<li><strong>图床配置名</strong>和<strong>设定仓库名</strong>填写创建的仓库名，格式：<code>用户名/仓库名</code></li>\n<li><strong>设定分支名</strong>，默认<code>main</code></li>\n<li><strong>获取Token：</strong><ul>\n<li>打开GitHub设置，找到 Developer settings</li>\n<li>点击 Personal access tokens 下的 Tokens（classic），如图所示创建token</li>\n<li><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/wiceee/myimg/img/image-20230110150325751.png\" alt=\"image-20230110150325751\"></li>\n<li><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/wiceee/myimg/img/image-20230110150736429.png\" alt=\"image-20230110150736429\"></li>\n<li>成功创建后，复制token（只会出现一次，做好记录）</li>\n<li><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/wiceee/myimg/img/image-20230110150948557.png\" alt=\"image-20230110150948557\"></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><strong>存储路径</strong>自定义即可，如<code>img/</code></li>\n<li>设定<strong>自定义域名</strong>：<code>https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/****/****</code>，后面的“****/****”为仓库名，<code>https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/</code>用来加速</li>\n<li>点击确定，再设置其为默认图床</li>\n<li><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/wiceee/myimg/img/image-20230110145949840.png\" alt=\"image-20230110145949840\"></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"MarkDown设置\"><a href=\"#MarkDown设置\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"MarkDown设置\"></a>MarkDown设置</h2><ul>\n<li>偏好设置&gt;图像，选择上传服务为<code>PicGo(app)</code>，设置PicGo安装路径，可点击验证图片上传选项</li>\n<li><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/wiceee/myimg/img/image-20230110151502705.png\" alt=\"image-20230110151502705\"></li>\n</ul>\n","text":"通过PicGo&amp;GitHub搭建个人图床下载PicGo 点击这里进入以下界面，点击releases 找到Assets点开，根据系统下载对应版本，我是Windows 10，下载的标有红框的版本 下载好后默认安装即可 创建GitHub仓库 新建一个仓库，用来存图片 设置Pic...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":574,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"blog","slug":"blog","count":4,"path":"api/categories/blog.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"blog","slug":"blog","count":2,"path":"api/tags/blog.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87PicGo-amp-GitHub%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%9B%BE%E5%BA%8A\"><span class=\"toc-text\">通过PicGo&amp;GitHub搭建个人图床</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BDPicGo\"><